        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2007-06-19T19:55:51Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Hate Crimes Against the Homeless Enforcement Act - Amends the Violent Crime Control and Law Enforcement Act of 1994 to revise the definition of &quot;hate crime&quot; to include a crime against an individual based on such individual's actual or perceived homeless status.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
